message.body: Whatchu got goin on in your rig? I was looking at the 50w orange bass amp, but figured id check what friends had first.
I got 2 15s that I built and a 150 watt 1970s Acoustic Control Corp SS head to match with spring reverb built in and a foot switch for the reverb
I'm probably gonna keep my sunn speakers and PA head, but I think I could part with the 2x15" speakers and acoustic control amp
Is the pic the one y built or the 1970
You could come play it if you want
How much $$
Potentially could come check it out Friday

The stained wood with paisley speaker cloth are the 15"s that I built. There are two of them. The amp is the one on the bottom that is black and the watts and ohms are matched to run the two 15" speakers
Partially looking for a bass amp for my bass but mostly to be running my electronics and vocals out of
I see

Well the sunn 4x12 PA speakers are better for full range but I need to record before I sell those. The 15s are full range Jensen speakers for bass/guitar/keyboard so they might serve your purpose but not as full range as PA speakers with cones and horns
You free Friday after work?
This might be more heavy duty than what I am looking for
Are u seeing the texts in sending u?
I'm*
I should be around Friday. No worries if it's not what your looking for.
Cool I will get in touch fri and hopefully come check it out.... Wasn't sure if u were gettig messages bc last week I tried to send u pics of my new house but they wouldn't go thru
But you should check it out. The spring reverb is pretty dope for experimental electronic stuff
